    • Method Detail

      • getDiscountType

        public int getDiscountType()
        Gets the discount type for this discount.
        Returns:
        The numerical code for the discount type. 1 = per item, 2 = per total number of items, 3 = per total cost.

      • getThreshold

        public int getThreshold()
        Gets the requirements for this discount.
        Returns:
        The requirement. If getDiscountType() == 1 it's the item identifier, if getDiscountType() == 2 it's the required number of items, if getDiscountType() == 3 it's the required total cost.
